45:19.351 --> 45:22.105
You want to talk about it?

45:22.105 --> 45:24.106
Not especially.

45:24.106 --> 45:26.567
- So what do you want me to do?
- What you came here for!

45:33.324 --> 45:36.911
There's this, uh...

45:36.911 --> 45:40.163
girl. Her name is Letha Godfrey.

45:42.164 --> 45:44.920
